# Exercise 7: If-Else Condition
# Write an if-else statement to check if a number is greater than or equal to 10
print("Exercise 7:")

# Define a number to check
number = 15

# If-Else condition to check if the number is greater than or equal to 10
if number >= 10:
    print(f"The number {number} is greater than or equal to 10.")
else:
    print(f"The number {number} is less than 10.")

